The "True Jesus Church" is an independent church that was established in 
Beijing, China in 1917. Today, there are approximately 1.5 million members in 
forty five countries. The church belongs to the Pentecostal branch of Christianity that emerged during the early Twentieth Century. Since 1990, the church was established in [[Samoa]]. They aim to preach the gospel to all nations before the Second Coming of Jesus. 

